The paper deals with a problem of collaboration among autonomous robots, which is a typical topic in the field of multi-agent systems (MAS) and robotics. Therefore, cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely categories. The paper also involves distributed algorithms and protocols, which are relevant to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of symmetry, which is a topic in the field of control theory and dynamical systems, and therefore cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category.
